%%{init: {'theme':'base','themeVariables':{'fontFamily':'Calibri','fontSize':'18px'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant SS as Sales Service
    participant MQ as Event Bus<br/>(RabbitMQ/Kafka)
    participant WD as Webhook Dispatcher
    participant CFG as Webhook Config DB
    participant EXT as Tenant External<br/>Endpoint
    participant DLQ as Dead Letter Queue
    participant RETRY as Retry Scheduler
    participant LOG as Webhook Log DB

    SS->>SS: Tạo đơn thành công (COMMIT)
    SS->>MQ: publish event<br/>{ type: order.created,<br/>orderId, tenantId, payload }
    MQ->>WD: consume event
    activate WD
    WD->>CFG: GET subscriptions<br/>WHERE event=order.created<br/>AND tenantId=?
    CFG-->>WD: [ { url, secret, headers } ]
    loop Mỗi subscription
      WD->>WD: Build HMAC-SHA256 signature<br/>với secret
      WD->>EXT: POST {url}<br/>X-Reborn-Signature: ...<br/>body=payload
      alt 2xx response
        EXT-->>WD: 200 OK
        WD->>LOG: INSERT status=SUCCESS
      else 4xx client error
        EXT-->>WD: 400 Bad Request
        WD->>LOG: INSERT status=FAILED_PERMANENT
      else 5xx / timeout
        EXT-->>WD: 500 / timeout
        WD->>LOG: INSERT status=RETRYING<br/>attempt=1
        WD->>DLQ: enqueue with delay<br/>(exp backoff 1m/5m/30m/2h)
      end
    end
    deactivate WD
    Note over DLQ,RETRY: Sau delay
    RETRY->>DLQ: poll
    DLQ-->>RETRY: failed message
    RETRY->>WD: re-dispatch
    alt Hết 5 lần retry
      WD->>LOG: status=FAILED_PERMANENT
      WD->>MQ: publish webhook.failed alert
    end
